WEBVTT

00:00:00.836 --> 00:00:03.384
[This talk contains mature content]

00:00:05.741 --> 00:00:07.361
Five years ago,

00:00:07.385 --> 00:00:10.639
I received a phone call
that would change my life.

00:00:11.795 --> 00:00:14.461
I remember so vividly that day.

00:00:15.245 --> 00:00:17.146
It was about this time of year,

00:00:17.170 --> 00:00:19.128
and I was sitting in my office.

00:00:19.692 --> 00:00:22.758
I remember the sun
streaming through the window.

00:00:23.592 --> 00:00:24.912
And my phone rang.

00:00:25.565 --> 00:00:26.752
And I picked it up,

00:00:27.594 --> 00:00:31.572
and it was two federal agents,
asking for my help